# Cookie Consent - Analytics & Marketing Tracking IDs
# These environment variables are used by the CookieConsent component
# to load tracking scripts when users consent to cookies.

# Google Analytics Measurement ID
# Get your ID from: https://analytics.google.com/ → Admin → Data Streams → Web
# Format: G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Meta (Facebook) Pixel ID
# Get your ID from: https://business.facebook.com/events_manager → Data Sources → Pixels
# Format: 15-digit number
NEXT_PUBLIC_META_PIXEL_ID=XXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

# Microsoft Clarity Project ID
# Get your ID from: https://clarity.microsoft.com/ → Project Settings
# Format: 10-character alphanumeric string
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLARITY_PROJECT_ID=XXXXXXXXXX

# Note: All tracking scripts are only loaded when users consent to the
# appropriate cookie categories (analytics or marketing) via the cookie banner.
